@page "/"

<PageTitle>Two Rooms</PageTitle>

<h1>Two Rooms</h1>
<p class="text-muted">
    Asymmetric co-op mini-games for two players. Join the same session code on two devices &mdash;
    you'll each see something different, so you'll need to talk to each other to win.
</p>

<div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-3 mt-2" style="max-width: 900px;">
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Reaction Duel</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Warm-up game. Both players see the same signal &mdash; first to react wins the round,
                    best of 5 takes the match.
                </p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="duel">Play Reaction Duel</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Maze Navigator</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    One player sees the maze but not their partner's position. The other can move
                    but can't see the map. Guide each other to the exit.
                </p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="maze">Play Maze Navigator</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
